{"tid":2151354,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"便衣警稱遭三青年襲擊 辯方指無表明身份 令人誤會是暴力藍絲","createTime":"2020-08-11T10:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T11:33:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a4988d0bf4b3cac499e240a32a53142e3f5a0a78","tid":2151354,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/OWUMBVCZENTBBJRA445K4N4SAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FOWUMBVCZENTBBJRA445K4N4SAM%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Ft6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=5676bb19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FOWUMBVCZENTBBJRA445K4N4SAM%2F&h=60fd76ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/OWUMBVCZENTBBJRA445K4N4SAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n市民去年10月在黃埔悼念浮屍海面的15歲女學生陳彥霖，一對年輕兄弟及18歲男生涉向馬路掟磚及以竹枝堵路，並襲擊便衣警致對方骨折。案件今續審，便衣警今承認當日與同袍均沒有表明身份，但辯稱當時因他正用盡全力制服被告，「體力上講唔到任何嘢」，又指「我相信我講係警察嘅話，會俾人打得更勁」。辯方則指，便衣警當時大叫「快啲嚟幫手」，令眾被告誤以為他是施暴藍絲，才反抗並控制他。便衣警不同意，惟承認有被告曾表明不想動武，多次要求他離開。"},{"pid":"c1c722ef5a272c28b5f16c841c14e0090ddfa302","tid":2151354,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:52:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6271bacf7a28c07a33258c9b43ebe0c3985a937","tid":2151354,"uid":183844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c1c722ef5a272c28b5f16c841c14e0090ddfa302","tid":2151354,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:52:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:54:45.000Z","msg":"要睇邊個官嘅"},{"pid":"d7e335a9308b1acb602004399aa1657e5eb0bf2e","tid":2151354,"uid":151313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:24:57.000Z","msg":"體力上講唔到野 連野都講唔到 仲有力制服？"},{"pid":"33ebcfc9d7541c6b64b640a669dd9f926c9bfe54","tid":2151354,"uid":137037,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7e335a9308b1acb602004399a